/a> hair, so you're guaranteed to find something to suit.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-62_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row" id="thick"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-63_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" id="glamorous" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-64_"><a data-link="inherit" href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/the-10-best-hair-accessories-for-christmas-2021#Index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-66_">Glamorous and glitzy hair accessories for winter</span></a></h2><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-67_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/glamorous-and-glitzy-hair-accessories-for-winter-1639585901128_1200x.jpg?v=1639585902" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/glamorous-and-glitzy-hair-accessories-for-winter-1639585901128.jpg?v=1639585902 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-68_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-70_">From shimmer and sequins to faux fur and sparkle, winter fashion gets us excited every year. Plus, whether you’re heading off to your work Christmas party or having a relaxed weekend with loved ones, the below ideas will never look out of place.&nbsp;</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-71_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-72_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-73_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-75_">Silk head scarves text.</span></h3><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-76_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti 